ConfigData.SQL: select LOTSN AS Barcode,Pmax AS PeakWat,FF AS FF,Voc AS Voc,Isc AS Isc,Vpm AS MaxVmpp,Ipm AS MaxImpp, ModuleAccessories.AccessorySn from DataChainDCIVResults with(nolock) inner join ModuleAccessories with(nolock) on DataChainDCIVResults.LotId = ModuleAccessories.LotId where LOTSN = @Barcode and isnew = 1
ConfigData.OracleSQL: select glass_sn Barcode,a.pmax PeakWat,a.ff FF,a.voc VOC,a.isc Isc,a.vm MaxVmpp,a.im MaxImpp,a.accessorysn AccessorySn from ia_002_tabmoduleinfo a where a.glass_sn= :Barcode
